"https://web.dev/learn/forms/auto#autocomplete"

"https://web.dev/learn/forms/autofill"
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
1. Use autofill. Browsers use heuristics to determine the address field for autofill form fills.

••Example:
<label for="email">Email</label>
<input type="email" name="email" id="email">

°°Example:
<main>
  <div class="wrapper">
    <form>
      <div>
        <label for="name">Name</label>
<input type="text" name="name" id="name" autocomplete="name">
      </div>
      <button>Save</button>
    </form>
  </div>
</main>

••CSS Value:
button {
  margin-top: 1rem;
}
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~